data.title: Golden State Warriors Roster
data.meta_description: Golden State Warriors scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
Andris Biedrins was selected as the #11 pick in the First Round of the 2004 NBA Draft by the Golden State Warriors. Andris Biedrins signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors on July 8, 2004.

Mike Dunleavy was selected as the #3 pick in the First Round of the 2002 NBA Draft by the Golden State Warriors. Mike Dunleavy signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors on July 7, 2002.

Adonal Foyle was selected as the #8 pick in the First Round of the 1997 NBA Draft by the Golden State Warriors. Adonal Foyle signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors on July 24, 1997. Adonal Foyle re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Golden State Warriors on August 3, 2000. Adonal Foyle re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Golden State Warriors on July 14, 2004.

Troy Murphy was selected as the #14 pick in the First Round of the 2001 NBA Draft by the Golden State Warriors. Troy Murphy signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors on August 24, 2001. Troy Murphy signed a multi-year extension with the Golden State Warriors on November 1, 2004.

Mickael Pietrus was selected as the #11 pick in the First Round of the 2003 NBA Draft by the Golden State Warriors. Mickael Pietrus signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors on July 7, 2003.
